44static int input_kex_gen_init(int, u_int32_t, struct ssh *);
45static int input_kex_gen_reply(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh);

47static int
48kex_gen_hash(
49 int hash_alg,
50 const struct sshbuf *client_version,
51 const struct sshbuf *server_version,
52 const struct sshbuf *client_kexinit,
53 const struct sshbuf *server_kexinit,
54 const struct sshbuf *server_host_key_blob,
55 const struct sshbuf *client_pub,
56 const struct sshbuf *server_pub,
57 const struct sshbuf *shared_secret,
58 u_char *hash, size_t *hashlen)
59{
60 struct sshbuf *b;
61 int r;
62
63 if (*hashlen < ssh_digest_bytes(hash_alg))
64 return SSH_ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT;
65 if ((b = sshbuf_new()) == NULL)
66 return SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
67 if ((r = sshbuf_put_stringb(b, client_version)) != 0 ||
68 (r = sshbuf_put_stringb(b, server_version)) != 0 ||
69 /* kexinit messages: fake header: len+SSH2_MSG_KEXINIT */
70 (r = sshbuf_put_u32(b, sshbuf_len(client_kexinit) + 1)) != 0 ||
71 (r = sshbuf_put_u8(b, SSH2_MSG_KEXINIT)) != 0 ||
72 (r = sshbuf_putb(b, client_kexinit)) != 0 ||
73 (r = sshbuf_put_u32(b, sshbuf_len(server_kexinit) + 1)) != 0 ||
74 (r = sshbuf_put_u8(b, SSH2_MSG_KEXINIT)) != 0 ||
75 (r = sshbuf_putb(b, server_kexinit)) != 0 ||
76 (r = sshbuf_put_stringb(b, server_host_key_blob)) != 0 ||
77 (r = sshbuf_put_stringb(b, client_pub)) != 0 ||
78 (r = sshbuf_put_stringb(b, server_pub)) != 0 ||
79 (r = sshbuf_putb(b, shared_secret)) != 0) {
80 sshbuf_free(b);
81 return r;
82 }
83#ifdef DEBUG_KEX
84 sshbuf_dump(b, stderr);
85#endif
86 if (ssh_digest_buffer(hash_alg, b, hash, *hashlen) != 0) {
87 sshbuf_free(b);
88 return SSH_ERR_LIBCRYPTO_ERROR;
89 }
90 sshbuf_free(b);
91 *hashlen = ssh_digest_bytes(hash_alg);
92#ifdef DEBUG_KEX
93 dump_digest("hash", hash, *hashlen);
94#endif
95 return 0;
96}
97
98int
99kex_gen_client(struct ssh *ssh)
100{
101 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
102 int r;
103
104 switch (kex->kex_type) {
105 case KEX_DH_GRP1_SHA1:
106 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA1:
107 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA256:
108 case KEX_DH_GRP16_SHA512:
109 case KEX_DH_GRP18_SHA512:
110 r = kex_dh_keypair(kex);
111 break;
112 case KEX_ECDH_SHA2:
113 r = kex_ecdh_keypair(kex);
114 break;
115 case KEX_C25519_SHA256:
116 r = kex_c25519_keypair(kex);
117 break;
118 case KEX_KEM_SNTRUP4591761X25519_SHA512:
119 r = kex_kem_sntrup4591761x25519_keypair(kex);
120 break;
121 default:
122 r = SSH_ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT;
123 break;
124 }
125 if (r != 0)
126 return r;
127 if ((r = sshpkt_start(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_ECDH_INIT)) != 0 ||
128 (r = sshpkt_put_stringb(ssh, kex->client_pub)) != 0 ||
129 (r = sshpkt_send(ssh)) != 0)
130 return r;
131 debug("expecting SSH2_MSG_KEX_ECDH_REPLY");
132 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_ECDH_REPLY, &input_kex_gen_reply);
133 return 0;
134}
135
136static int
137input_kex_gen_reply(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh)
138{
139 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
140 struct sshkey *server_host_key = NULL;
141 struct sshbuf *shared_secret = NULL;
142 struct sshbuf *server_blob = NULL;
143 struct sshbuf *tmp = NULL, *server_host_key_blob = NULL;
144 u_char *signature = NULL;
145 u_char hash[SSH_DIGEST_MAX_LENGTH];
146 size_t slen, hashlen;
147 int r;
148
149 /* hostkey */
150 if ((r = sshpkt_getb_froms(ssh, &server_host_key_blob)) != 0)
151 goto out;
152 /* sshkey_fromb() consumes its buffer, so make a copy */
153 if ((tmp = sshbuf_fromb(server_host_key_blob)) == NULL) {
154 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
155 goto out;
156 }
157 if ((r = sshkey_fromb(tmp, &server_host_key)) != 0)
158 goto out;
159 if ((r = kex_verify_host_key(ssh, server_host_key)) != 0)
160 goto out;
161
162 /* Q_S, server public key */
163 /* signed H */
164 if ((r = sshpkt_getb_froms(ssh, &server_blob)) != 0 ||
165 (r = sshpkt_get_string(ssh, &signature, &slen)) != 0 ||
166 (r = sshpkt_get_end(ssh)) != 0)
167 goto out;
168
169 /* compute shared secret */
170 switch (kex->kex_type) {
171 case KEX_DH_GRP1_SHA1:
172 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA1:
173 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA256:
174 case KEX_DH_GRP16_SHA512:
175 case KEX_DH_GRP18_SHA512:
176 r = kex_dh_dec(kex, server_blob, &shared_secret);
177 break;
178 case KEX_ECDH_SHA2:
179 r = kex_ecdh_dec(kex, server_blob, &shared_secret);
180 break;
181 case KEX_C25519_SHA256:
182 r = kex_c25519_dec(kex, server_blob, &shared_secret);
183 break;
184 case KEX_KEM_SNTRUP4591761X25519_SHA512:
185 r = kex_kem_sntrup4591761x25519_dec(kex, server_blob,
186 &shared_secret);
187 break;
188 default:
189 r = SSH_ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT;
190 break;
191 }
192 if (r !=0 )
193 goto out;
194
195 /* calc and verify H */
196 hashlen = sizeof(hash);
197 if ((r = kex_gen_hash(
198 kex->hash_alg,
199 kex->client_version,
200 kex->server_version,
201 kex->my,
202 kex->peer,
203 server_host_key_blob,
204 kex->client_pub,
205 server_blob,
206 shared_secret,
207 hash, &hashlen)) != 0)
208 goto out;
209
210 if ((r = sshkey_verify(server_host_key, signature, slen, hash, hashlen,
211 kex->hostkey_alg, ssh->compat)) != 0)
212 goto out;
213
214 if ((r = kex_derive_keys(ssh, hash, hashlen, shared_secret)) == 0)
215 r = kex_send_newkeys(ssh);
216out:
217 explicit_bzero(hash, sizeof(hash));
218 explicit_bzero(kex->c25519_client_key, sizeof(kex->c25519_client_key));
219 explicit_bzero(kex->sntrup4591761_client_key,
220 sizeof(kex->sntrup4591761_client_key));
221 sshbuf_free(server_host_key_blob);
222 free(signature);
223 sshbuf_free(tmp);
224 sshkey_free(server_host_key);
225 sshbuf_free(server_blob);
226 sshbuf_free(shared_secret);
227 sshbuf_free(kex->client_pub);
228 kex->client_pub = NULL;
229 return r;
230}
231
232int
233kex_gen_server(struct ssh *ssh)
234{
235 debug("expecting SSH2_MSG_KEX_ECDH_INIT");
236 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_ECDH_INIT, &input_kex_gen_init);
237 return 0;
238}
239
240static int
241input_kex_gen_init(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh)
242{
243 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
244 struct sshkey *server_host_private, *server_host_public;
245 struct sshbuf *shared_secret = NULL;
246 struct sshbuf *server_pubkey = NULL;
247 struct sshbuf *client_pubkey = NULL;
248 struct sshbuf *server_host_key_blob = NULL;
249 u_char *signature = NULL, hash[SSH_DIGEST_MAX_LENGTH];
250 size_t slen, hashlen;
251 int r;
252
253 if ((r = kex_load_hostkey(ssh, &server_host_private,
254 &server_host_public)) != 0)
255 goto out;
256
257 if ((r = sshpkt_getb_froms(ssh, &client_pubkey)) != 0 ||
258 (r = sshpkt_get_end(ssh)) != 0)
259 goto out;
260
261 /* compute shared secret */
262 switch (kex->kex_type) {
263 case KEX_DH_GRP1_SHA1:
264 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA1:
265 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA256:
266 case KEX_DH_GRP16_SHA512:
267 case KEX_DH_GRP18_SHA512:
268 r = kex_dh_enc(kex, client_pubkey, &server_pubkey,
269 &shared_secret);
270 break;
271 case KEX_ECDH_SHA2:
272 r = kex_ecdh_enc(kex, client_pubkey, &server_pubkey,
273 &shared_secret);
274 break;
275 case KEX_C25519_SHA256:
276 r = kex_c25519_enc(kex, client_pubkey, &server_pubkey,
277 &shared_secret);
278 break;
279 case KEX_KEM_SNTRUP4591761X25519_SHA512:
280 r = kex_kem_sntrup4591761x25519_enc(kex, client_pubkey,
281 &server_pubkey, &shared_secret);
282 break;
283 default:
284 r = SSH_ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT;
285 break;
286 }
287 if (r !=0 )
288 goto out;
289
290 /* calc H */
291 if ((server_host_key_blob = sshbuf_new()) == NULL) {
292 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
293 goto out;
294 }
295 if ((r = sshkey_putb(server_host_public, server_host_key_blob)) != 0)
296 goto out;
297 hashlen = sizeof(hash);
298 if ((r = kex_gen_hash(
299 kex->hash_alg,
300 kex->client_version,
301 kex->server_version,
302 kex->peer,
303 kex->my,
304 server_host_key_blob,
305 client_pubkey,
306 server_pubkey,
307 shared_secret,
308 hash, &hashlen)) != 0)
309 goto out;
310
311 /* sign H */
312 if ((r = kex->sign(ssh, server_host_private, server_host_public,
313 &signature, &slen, hash, hashlen, kex->hostkey_alg)) != 0)
314 goto out;
315
316 /* send server hostkey, ECDH pubkey 'Q_S' and signed H */
317 if ((r = sshpkt_start(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_ECDH_REPLY)) != 0 ||
318 (r = sshpkt_put_stringb(ssh, server_host_key_blob)) != 0 ||
319 (r = sshpkt_put_stringb(ssh, server_pubkey)) != 0 ||
320 (r = sshpkt_put_string(ssh, signature, slen)) != 0 ||
321 (r = sshpkt_send(ssh)) != 0)
322 goto out;
323
324 if ((r = kex_derive_keys(ssh, hash, hashlen, shared_secret)) == 0)
325 r = kex_send_newkeys(ssh);
326out:
327 explicit_bzero(hash, sizeof(hash));
328 sshbuf_free(server_host_key_blob);
329 free(signature);
330 sshbuf_free(shared_secret);
331 sshbuf_free(client_pubkey);
332 sshbuf_free(server_pubkey);
333 return r;
334}
